{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveSPredEntails\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">solveSPredEntails</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Break down `H ⊢ₛ T` as far as possible, reporting `none` when no progress was made.\n1. If `H` is pure `⌜φ₁⌝`, turn the goal into `h : φ₁ ⊢ ⊢ₛ T`.\n2. If *also* `T` is pure `⌜φ₂⌝`, turn the goal into `h : φ₁ ⊢ φ₂`, then exit.\n3. Otherwise, `H` or `T` was not pure. We continue by introducing all state variables,\n   `H s₁ ... sₙ ⊢ₛ T s₁ ... sₙ`. For a monomorphic monad stack, this will an entailment on\n  `SPred []`. If either `H` or `T` was pure, `⌜·⌝`, state introduction preserves this.\n4. Finally, turn `H ⊢ₛ T` into `h : H.down ⊢ T.down` (at `SPred []`).\n5. If either `T` was pure `⌜φ₂⌝` (and `H` was not), we turn `T.down` into `φ₂`.\n   (NB: If `H` was pure, then we have already lifted `φ₁` to the local context.)\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveSPredEntails","kind":"def","line":113,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveSPredEntails","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L113-L189"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.neededStateIntro\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">neededStateIntro</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">thm</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.SpecAttr.SpecTheoremNew\">SpecAttr.SpecTheoremNew</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">excessArgs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.neededStateIntro","kind":"def","line":101,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.neededStateIntro","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L101-L111"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.consIntroAndSimpStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">consIntroAndSimpStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Apply `SPred.entails_cons_intro` to introduce one state variable, then `introsSimp`,\nthen peel a leading `SPred.pure (σ::σs) φ s` from each side of `⊢ₛ` via\n`apply_pure_cons_entails_l/r`. Returns `none` if no `entails_cons_intro` was applicable.\n\nPerforms the pure-cons cleanup at the exact iteration the state variable is introduced,\nso the goal stays in canonical form throughout the eta-expansion loop.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.consIntroAndSimpStep","kind":"def","line":83,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.consIntroAndSimpStep","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L83-L99"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solvePostCondEntails\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">solvePostCondEntails</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solvePostCondEntails","kind":"def","line":59,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solvePostCondEntails","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L59-L81"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveExceptCondsEntails\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">solveExceptCondsEntails</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveExceptCondsEntails","kind":"def","line":42,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveExceptCondsEntails","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L42-L56"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.tripleOfWP\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">tripleOfWP</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Unfold `⦃P⦄ x ⦃Q⦄` into `P ⊢ₛ wp⟦x⟧ Q` by applying `Tiple.of_wp`, ensuring that `PostShape.args ps`\nis reduced.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.tripleOfWP","kind":"def","line":28,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.tripleOfWP","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L28-L39"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Util","Lean.Meta.Sym.Util"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Entails"}